MEDICAL DISCLAIMER

This tool is intended for research and clinical reference purposes only.
It is designed to assist qualified medical and pharmacy personnel in the
preparation of Carnoy's solution as a surgical adjunct in oral and
maxillofacial surgery.

- All compounding decisions must be validated and approved by a licensed
  medical professional familiar with the clinical context.
- The formulation parameters (ratios, tolerances) are based on published
  literature and are provided for reference only.
- The author and contributors assume no liability for any clinical outcomes,
  adverse events, or errors resulting from the use of this software.
- This software is NOT a substitute for institutional pharmacy protocols,
